<TUV xml:lang='en-US'>($07) RequestEmissionRelatedDTCsDetectedDuringCurrentOrLastCompletedCycle</TUV>
</NAME>
<DESC>
<TUV xml:lang='en-US'>The purpose of this service is to enable the external test equipment to obtain "pending" diagnostic trouble codes detected during current or last completed driving cycle for emission-related components / systems that are tested or continuously monitored during normal driving conditions (assist service technician afer a vehicle repair, and after clearing diagnostic information, by reporting test results after a single drivingcycle)</TUV>
</DESC>
