</NAME>
<DESC>
<TUV xml:lang='en-US'>The pupose of this service is to enable external test equipment to control the operation of an on-board sytem, test or component. This specific sub-service is responsible for transfering the TID data of the supported TIDs. This sub-service allows all TIDs, except of $00, $20, $40, $60, ....</TUV>
