<NAME>
<TUV xml:lang='en-US'>InfoType</TUV>
</NAME>
<DESC>
<TUV xml:lang='en-US'>The InfoTypes $00, $20, $40, $60, $80, $A0, $C0, $E0 result in an response that contains the supported InfoTypes in the respective range (e.g. $40 -&#62; response describes the InfoTypes in range $41-$60.
Note, in this case one InfoType is mandatory and at most 6 InfoTypes are allowed.
Each other InfoType results in a response that contains the corresponding InfoType data.</TUV>
</DESC>
<QUAL>InfoType</QUAL>
</STATICCOMP>
</REQ>
