<TEXT>
<TUV xml:lang='en-US'>
1/Level_A:32PP13 2 SC PSU Vout1 Exceeds the range

2/Level_A:32PP13 2 SC PSU Vout2 Exceeds the range


</TUV>
</TEXT>
<TRRECORDITEM idref='_0000020D2471F0C0'>
<TEXT>
<TUV xml:lang='en-US'>The 1/Vout1 voltage is 94% higher than Vbat and 6% lower than Vbat, and the duration is 10ms
The 2/Vout2 voltage is 94% higher than Vbat and 6% lower than Vbat, and the duration is 10ms</TUV>
</TEXT>
</TRRECORDITEM>
<TRRECORDITEM idref='_0000020D2471E7C0'>
<TEXT>
<TUV xml:lang='en-US'>1/Vout1 voltage at [10%,90%] of Vbat, duration 10ms
