<TEXT>
<TUV xml:lang='en-US'>
1/Level_A: Motor current sampling bias fault
2/Level_A:A4911 is faulty
3/Level_A: The A4911 SPI communication fails
4/Level_A:A4911 Self-test VBRG open circuit
5/Level_A:A4911 Self-check Phase A state
6/Level_A:A4911 Self-check Phase B state
7/Level_A:A4911 Self-check Phase C state
8/Level_A:A4911 Self-check Sense amp 1 disconnect
9/Level_A:A4911 Self-check Sense amp 2 disconnect
10/Level_A:A4911 Self-check Sense amp 3 disconnect
11/Level_A:A4911 Self-check LSSA disconnect
12/Level_A:A4911 Self-check LSSB disconnect
13/Level_A:A4911 Self-check LSSC disconnect
14/Level_A:A4911 Self-check VREG out of range
15/Level_A:A4911 Self-check VREG Undervoltage
16/Level_A:A4911 Self-check VREG Overvoltage
17/Level_A:A4911 Indicates a High temperature warning
18/Level_A:A4911 Self-checks Over temperature
19/Level_A:A4911 Self-check VBB out of range
20/Level_A:A4911 Self-check VBB Overvoltage
21/Level_A:A4911 Self-check VBB Undervoltage
22/Level_A:A4911 Self-check VGS undervoltage
23/Level_A:A4911 Self-test Phase A low-side VGS undervoltage
24/Level_A:A4911 Self-test Phase A high-side VGS undervoltage
25/Level_A:A4911 Self-test Phase B low-side VGS undervoltage
