<TEXT>
<TUV xml:lang='en-US'>1/Level_A: System power supply voltage Vdiode A-level Com undervoltage

2/Level_A: The system power supply voltage Vdiode level A Com is overvoltage

3/Level_A: Pull up the Valve, EPB, and external power supply. The KL30V power supply overvoltage

4/Level_A: The motor power supply VLINK overvoltage

5/Level_A:35584 The 3V3 power supply to the MCU is underpowered

6/Level_A:35584 The 3V3 power supply to the MCU is overvoltage

7/Level_A:PSV1, CSV, SSV1 Three Valve power supplies VSW2_VAL Undervoltage (BE13)

8/Level_A:PSV1, CSV, SSV1 Three Valve power supplies VSW2_VAL Overvoltage (BE13)

9/Level_A: Valve Power undervoltage (BE13_2)

10/Level_A: Valve Power supply overvoltage (BE13_2)

11/Level_A:VSW3VAL Undervoltage

12/Level_A:VSW3VAL Overvoltage

13/Level_A: master cylinder pressure sensor power supply V5_HPS_MC undervoltage

14/Level_A: master cylinder pressure sensor power supply V5_HPS_MC overvoltage

15/Level_A:G sensor Power supply 3V3_GS Undervoltage

16/Level_A:G sensor Power supply 3V3_GS overvoltage
</TUV>
</TEXT>
