<TEXT>
<TUV xml:lang='en-US'>1/Level_A: Rear right wheel BE13 RR short to battery fault

2/Level_A: indicates the BE13 RR reverse current fault of the rear right wheel
</TUV>
</TEXT>
<TRRECORDITEM idref='_0000020D2471F0C0'>
<TEXT>
<TUV xml:lang='en-US'>1/ Rear right wheel BE13 RR current below 4.9mA(4.025-5.7mA) for 586us(464-720us, WS1 off, debounce 120ms
