</TUV>
</TEXT>
<TRRECORDITEM idref='_0000020D2471F0C0'>
<TEXT>
<TUV xml:lang='en-US'>1/4 of 4 wheels will result in an untrusted wheel speed fault when any two wheels have a fault that causes the wheel speed to be untrusted
